pizzas.title: Bolognese pizza
pizzas.desciption: The Bolognese pizza is spread with a traditional tomato pizza base, then we put bolognese sauce on it

pizzas.title: Ham-mushroom pizza
pizzas.desciption: Ham and mushroom pizza is made with a tomato pizza base. Ham and chive mushrooms, with corn and cheese

pizzas.title: Bulldozer pizza

pizzas.desciption: The corn pizza is a real gentle pizza, vegetarians can also enjoy it. Corn pizza with tomato base
